    title: 'Local-First Collaborative Apps',
    description:
      'Build applications where IndexedDB is the primary database, not just a cache. Create instantaneous experiences with zero loading states.',
    example: 'Design tools like Figma, document editors, team workspaces',
  },
  {
    title: 'High-Performance Caching',
    description:
      'Transform traditional web apps with intelligent data caching. Use complex queries to filter and sort cached API responses client-side.',
